&lt;p&gt;You can also deploy your React app to Github. But, I will cover that in another article.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Happy Hacking!&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[How to create a static blog using Gatsby]]></title><description><![CDATA[A tutorial on creating a static blog using Gatsby and creating a new post]]></description><link>https://lumen.netlify.composts/how-to-create-a-static-blog-using-gatsby/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://lumen.netlify.composts/how-to-create-a-static-blog-using-gatsby/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2019 21:26:56 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;There are many static site generators available. But I felt Gatsby is very easy to learn and maintain.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this tutorial, we will learn&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Getting Started&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Select Starter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creating a new post&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run &amp;#x26; build the blog&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;getting-started&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#getting-started&quot; aria-label=&quot;getting started permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Getting Started&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Install &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;gatsby-cli&lt;/code&gt; using this command&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; -g gatsby-cli&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;select-starter&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#select-starter&quot; aria-label=&quot;select starter permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Select Starter&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are multiple starters available at Gatsby. I love the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/alxshelepenok/gatsby-starter-lumen&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;lumen starter&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/alxshelepenok&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;@Alexander Shelepenok&lt;/a&gt; which is used in building this site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Install starter using this command&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;shell&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-shell&quot;&gt;gatsby new blog https://github.com/alxshelepenok/gatsby-starter-lumen&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will create a &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;blog&lt;/code&gt; folder with this structure&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;└── content
    ├── pages
    └── posts
└── static
    ├── admin
    └── media
└── src
    ├── assets
    │   └── scss
    │       ├── base
    │       └── mixins
    ├── cms
    │   └── preview-templates
    ├── components
    │   ├── Feed
    │   ├── Icon
    │   ├── Layout
    │   ├── Page
    │   ├── Pagination
    │   ├── Post
    │   │   ├── Author
    │   │   ├── Comments
    │   │   ├── Content
    │   │   ├── Meta
    │   │   └── Tags
    │   └── Sidebar
    │       ├── Author
